We are so excited to announce that our baby boys are finally here!!!

At 5:31am Friday morning, Ezra Raye Bishop came through at 6lbs 2oz. 

Then at 5:41am, Easyn Ron Bishop came through at 6lbs 13oz.

We have two beautiful healthy boys and momma is doing great! I admire my wife so much! She was a trooper and is truly my superwoman! She labored throughout the night, but pushed the boys out within 20min! CRAZY!!! She truly embodies a woman of strength, courage and determination! I’m so so so proud of you honey! You did wonderful and are continuing to do amazing! I love you so much! 

Shout out to my mom, mother-in-love and sister for being there with us! We love and appreciate you guys to the fullest!

God is so good! We are so grateful to Him and all He has in store for us!

This past year has been one for the books. I was able to push myself more than ever, with purpose and intentionality; and I’m grateful to see these numbers compared to last year. The grind I’ve put in with absolutely no backing, no label, nobody to “put me on” or “push me”, I’m definitely proud to see the fruit from what God has gifted me to do in this music industry. 

Numbers are numbers. I get this may not be much to some people, but all I can do is think about where I come from and how far I’ve come. I can’t do anything, but thank God. I appreciate all of you who have purchased, streamed and downloaded my music. I don’t take it lightly! Please continue to support and pray for me as I prepare for the next stages of my career! Seen you soon 2024! 💪🏾💪🏾💪🏾

#coreyronell #spotifywrapped #grateful

2023 personally, was a year of growth for me. Took on new opportunities, made leaps and stepped out on faith in my career, and took some losses along the way. But it was all preparing me for this new year. I’m excited and looking forward to every new door of opportunity God allows me to walk through. It’s time to be focused and STAY READY. 

I give God all the glory for everything He’s done and for the things he’s going to do. There’s nobody like Him! I’m so grateful!

Happy Heavenly Birthday chief! Man, not a day goes by that I don’t think about you. Always wondering how you would’ve handled certain things or just having your business sense. We all miss you so much. It’s still so weird, even though it’s almost been 6 years. 

Continue watching over us until we see you again. Just know your legacy continues to live through us and your grandchildren. I love you chief!!! Miss you incredibly!

Happy Birthday!

“Better” streaming on all DSP’s!!! Go run it up! Happy Sunday. ☺️
